<D>__{i've heard enough of my safety... what about my father?... i heard you talking. you speak as if he was dead. well, he isn't!}
<C>__{jessica}
<D>__{paul!}
<A>__{she tries to hold him.}
<C>__{paul}
<D>__{well he isn't... and he won't die... tell me he won't die!}
<C>__{reverend mother}
<D>__{what can be done has been done.}
<C>__{paul}
<D>__{mother! tell me!}
<A>__{the reverend mother covers herself and moves quickly to the door. }
